      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Kristian Kersting</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"/File:KristianKersting.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/3f/KristianKersting.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:KristianKersting.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Kristian Kersting <sup id=\"cite_ref-Kersting_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Kersting-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Kristian Kersting</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist and professor at Computer Science Department, <a href=\"/Darmstadt_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Darmstadt University of Technology\">TU Darmstadt</a> and head of its Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning (AIML) lab <sup id=\"cite_ref-Kersting_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Kersting-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe received his Ph.D. from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Freiburg\">University of Freiburg</a> on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inductive_logic_programming\">inductive logic programming</a> in 2006 under advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>,\nand had appointments at <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">MIT</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fraunhofer-Institut_f%C3%BCr_Intelligente_Analyse-_und_Informationssysteme\">Fraunhofer IAIS</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bonn\">University of Bonn</a>, and <a href=\"/University_of_Dortmund\" title=\"University of Dortmund\">TU Dortmund</a>.\nHis main research interests are in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_relational_learning\">statistical relational learning</a> and <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, and <a href=\"/Deep_Learning\" title=\"Deep Learning\">deep learning</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#CrazyAra\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">CrazyAra</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"CrazyAra\">CrazyAra</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: CrazyAra\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Along with <a href=\"/Johannes_F%C3%BCrnkranz\" title=\"Johannes Fürnkranz\">Johannes Fürnkranz</a> at TU Darmstadt, Kristian Kersting led the <i>Deep Learning: Methods and Architectures</i> course in 2018, and supported his students <a href=\"/Johannes_Czech\" title=\"Johannes Czech\">Johannes Czech</a>, <a href=\"/Moritz_Willig\" title=\"Moritz Willig\">Moritz Willig</a> and <a href=\"/Alena_Beyer\" title=\"Alena Beyer\">Alena Beyer</a> in developing \nthe deep learning <a href=\"/Chess#Variants\" title=\"Chess\">chess variant</a> engine <a href=\"/CrazyAra\" title=\"CrazyAra\">CrazyAra</a>, which won a five game <a href=\"/Crazyhouse\" title=\"Crazyhouse\">Crazyhouse</a> online-match versus <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Tan\">Justin Tan</a> aka JannLee with 4-1 \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nSubsequently, he worked with his students Johannes Czech and <a href=\"/Patrick_Korus\" title=\"Patrick Korus\">Patrick Korus</a> on an improvement of <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero's</a> <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">MCTS</a> / <a href=\"/Christopher_D._Rosin#PUCT\" title=\"Christopher D. Rosin\">PUCT</a> algorithm considering <a href=\"/Transposition\" title=\"Transposition\">transpositions</a>, optionally applied in CrazyAra.\nThe proposed <b>Monte-Carlo Graph Search</b> uses a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Directed_acyclic_graph\">directed acyclic graph</a> (DAG) rather than a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tree_structure\">tree structure</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Bayesian Logic Programs</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/cs/0111058\">arXiv:cs/0111058</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-44797-0_9\">Adaptive Bayesian Logic Programs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/ilp/ilp2001.html#KerstingR01a\">ILP 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-44797-0_10\">Towards Combining Inductive Logic Programming with Bayesian Networks</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/ilp/ilp2001.html#KerstingR01a\">ILP 2001</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Probabilistic logic learning</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://kdd.org/explorations/P30\">SIGKDD Explorations</a>, Vol. 5, No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/kersting/pll_icml04/pll.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lirias.kuleuven.be/1992259?limo=0\">Logical Markov Decision Programs and the Convergence of Logical TD(lambda)</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/ilp/ilp2004.html#KerstingR04\">ILP 2004</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/kersting/papers/ilp04.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-78652-8_1\">Probabilistic Inductive Logic Programming</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/alt/alt2004.html#RaedtK04\">ALT 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/kersting/FAIAilpsrl/\">An Inductive Logic Programming Approach to Statistical Relational Learning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.iospress.nl/bookserie/frontiers-in-artificial-intelligence-and-applications/\">Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence and Applications</a>, Vol. 148</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-78652-8_1\">Probabilistic Inductive Logic Programming</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>, Vol. 4911</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2010, 2017</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F978-0-387-30164-8_786\">Statistical Relational Learning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/referencework/10.1007/978-0-387-30164-8\">Encyclopedia of Machine Learning and Data Mining</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Lifted Probabilistic Inference</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/ecai/ecai2012.html#Kersting12\">ECAI 2012</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sfb876.tu-dortmund.de/PublicPublicationFiles/kersting_2012a.pdf\">pdf</a>\t</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=f9iP-80AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Christian Bauckhage</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Efficient Information Theoretic Clustering on Discrete Lattices</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1310.7114\">arXiv:1310.7114</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=f9iP-80AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Christian Bauckhage</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.de/citations?user=WDHoQtYAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Christian Thurau</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://publica.fraunhofer.de/dokumente/N-351724.html\">Künstliche Intelligenz für Computerspiele - Historische Entwicklung und aktuelle Trends</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Informatik_Spektrum\">Informatik Spektrum</a>, Vol. 37, No. 6 (German)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#SNatarajan\" title=\"Mathematician\">Sriraam Natarajan</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#DPoole\" title=\"Mathematician\">David Poole</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.morganclaypool.com/doi/10.2200/S00692ED1V01Y201601AIM032\">Statistical Relational Artificial Intelligence: Logic, Probability, and Computation</a></i>.  Synthesis Lectures on Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.morganclaypool.com/\">Morgan &amp; Claypool Publishers</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13218-018-0562-8\">Making AI Smarter</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/journal/13218\">Künstliche Intelligenz</a>, Vol. 32, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fdata.2018.00006/full\">Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence: Two Fellow Travelers on the Quest for Intelligent Behavior in Machines</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/big-data#\">Frontiers in Big Data</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Johannes_Czech\" title=\"Johannes Czech\">Johannes Czech</a>, <a href=\"/Moritz_Willig\" title=\"Moritz Willig\">Moritz Willig</a>, <a href=\"/Alena_Beyer\" title=\"Alena Beyer\">Alena Beyer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Johannes_F%C3%BCrnkranz\" title=\"Johannes Fürnkranz\">Johannes Fürnkranz</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>Learning to play the Chess Variant Crazyhouse above World Champion Level with Deep Neural Networks and Human Data</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1908.06660\">arXiv:1908.06660</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Johannes_Czech\" title=\"Johannes Czech\">Johannes Czech</a>, <a href=\"/Moritz_Willig\" title=\"Moritz Willig\">Moritz Willig</a>, <a href=\"/Alena_Beyer\" title=\"Alena Beyer\">Alena Beyer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/Johannes_F%C3%BCrnkranz\" title=\"Johannes Fürnkranz\">Johannes Fürnkranz</a> (<b>2020</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/frai.2020.00024/full\">Learning to Play the Chess Variant Crazyhouse Above World Champion Level With Deep Neural Networks and Human Data</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/artificial-intelligence#\">Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2020</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13218-020-00692-5\">Rethinking Computer Science Through AI</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/journal/13218\">Künstliche Intelligenz</a>, Vol. 34, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Johannes_Czech\" title=\"Johannes Czech\">Johannes Czech</a>, <a href=\"/Patrick_Korus\" title=\"Patrick Korus\">Patrick Korus</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2020</b>). <i>Monte-Carlo Graph Search for AlphaZero</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2012.11045\">arXiv:2012.11045</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Johannes_Czech\" title=\"Johannes Czech\">Johannes Czech</a>, <a href=\"/Patrick_Korus\" title=\"Patrick Korus\">Patrick Korus</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a> (<b>2021</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ojs.aaai.org/index.php/ICAPS/article/view/15952\">Improving AlphaZero Using Monte-Carlo Graph Search</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ojs.aaai.org/index.php/ICAPS/issue/view/380\">Proceedings of the Thirty-First International Conference on Automated Planning and Scheduling</a>, Vol. 31, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ml.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de/papers/czech2021icaps_mcgs.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de/fb20/organisation_fb20/professuren_und_gruppenleitungen/fb20professuren_und_gruppenleitungen_detailseite_36544.de.jsp\">Kristian Kersting – Informatik – Technische Universität Darmstadt</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ml-research.github.io/people/kkersting/index.html\">Kristian Kersting</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www-ai.cs.tu-dortmund.de/auto?self=%24dw3ljibgu8\">Prof. Dr. Kristian Kersting</a>, <a href=\"/University_of_Dortmund\" title=\"University of Dortmund\">TU Dortmund</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=QY-earAAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">‪Kristian Kersting‬ - ‪Google Scholar‬</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nachrichten.idw-online.de/2019/02/19/schachmatt-durch-crazyara-kuenstliche-intelligenz-schlaegt-mehrfachen-weltmeister-im-einsetzschach/\">Schachmatt durch CrazyAra: Künstliche Intelligenz schlägt mehrfachen Weltmeister im Einsetzschach</a> by  <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kristian Kersting</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Informationsdienst_Wissenschaft\">Informationsdienst Wissenschaft</a>, February 19, 2019 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.welt.de/wirtschaft/bilanz/article202860588/Sieger-des-deutschen-KI-Preises-Der-Traum-von-der-starken-KI.html\">Sieger des deutschen KI-Preises: Der Traum von der starken KI</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://muckrack.com/christian-buck\">Christian Buck</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Die_Welt\">Welt</a>, November 02, 2019</li>\n<li> Kristian Kersting - Making deep neural networks right for the right scientific reasons, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://digicrop.de/\">DIGICROP 2020</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/wSO04nHQEXc?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kristian_Kersting&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Kersting-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Kersting_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Kersting_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ml-research.github.io/people/kkersting/index.html\">Kristian Kersting</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://zhchess.blogspot.com/2018/12/crazyara-plays-jannlee-for-christmas.html\">Crazyhouse Chess: CrazyAra plays JannLee for Christmas</a>, December 26, 2018</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nachrichten.idw-online.de/2019/02/19/schachmatt-durch-crazyara-kuenstliche-intelligenz-schlaegt-mehrfachen-weltmeister-im-einsetzschach/\">Schachmatt durch CrazyAra: Künstliche Intelligenz schlägt mehrfachen Weltmeister im Einsetzschach</a> by  <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink